{"id":425,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":27,"title":"27. A New Baby","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":10,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby.425/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/0-27-a-new-baby.mp3","transcript":"Well, hello, Mr Wallace.\nYou seem unusually happy today.\nI just became a father!\nCongratulations. A boy or a girl?\nYou never saw such a cute girl.\nNine pounds, three ounces... and as cute as a button.\nDoesn't this call for cigars?\nOh, yes. I forgot about the cigars. Here, have one.\nThank you. How's your wife?\nShe's just fine.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:36","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Well, hello, Mr Wallace.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/1.mp3","time_start":1.73,"time_end":3.91},{"position":2,"content":"You seem unusually happy today.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/2.mp3","time_start":3.91,"time_end":5.79},{"position":3,"content":"I just became a father!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/3.mp3","time_start":5.79,"time_end":7.21},{"position":4,"content":"Congratulations. A boy or a girl?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/4.mp3","time_start":7.21,"time_end":9.56},{"position":5,"content":"You never saw such a cute girl.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/5.mp3","time_start":9.56,"time_end":11.72},{"position":6,"content":"Nine pounds, three ounces... and as cute as a button.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/6.mp3","time_start":11.72,"time_end":14.76},{"position":7,"content":"Doesn't this call for cigars?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/7.mp3","time_start":14.76,"time_end":16.27},{"position":8,"content":"Oh, yes. I forgot about the cigars. Here, have one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/8.mp3","time_start":16.27,"time_end":19.44},{"position":9,"content":"Thank you. How's your wife?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/9.mp3","time_start":19.44,"time_end":21.1},{"position":10,"content":"She's just fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/27-a-new-baby-2022-03-07-21-13-19/10.mp3","time_start":21.13,"time_end":22.28}]}